DTSTART;TZID=Europe/Tallinn:20260721T100000
DTEND;TZID=Europe/Tallinn:20260721T104500
LOCATION:Energiakeskus Studio\, Tallinn
DESCRIPTION:Status: DONE\nWho: Jeffrey Allen\, Kaitlin O'Toole\, Nadir Salam\nMOVED to 10:00 at Jeffrey's request (email 14 Jul): he collects Hisami from TLL (lands 7:30am)\, so a 9am start was too tight. Pushed John Lee's interview to 11:00 to clear the slot. Day before his 4-block stage day.\nFull schedule: https://garethwinter-cpu.github.io/mindvalley-u-production/
END:VEVENT
