LOCATION:Energiakeskus Studio\, Tallinn
DESCRIPTION:Who: Paul McKenna\, Kaitlin O'Toole\, Nadir Salam\nCONFIRMED BY AUTHOR (Paul McKenna\, email 14 Jul). NUDGED 12:00→12:15 (16 Jul): Kaitlin is MC'ing the main stage until 12:00 (Jim Kwik session)\, so she can't start at 12:00. Now straight after she comes off stage — she's already in hair/makeup from hosting (no separate glam)\, just Paul gets a touch-up. Keeps Kaitlin as interviewer per Gareth.\nFull schedule: https://garethwinter-cpu.github.io/mindvalley-u-production/
