DTSTART;TZID=Europe/Tallinn:20260731T144500
DTEND;TZID=Europe/Tallinn:20260731T153000
LOCATION:Energiakeskus Studio\, Tallinn
DESCRIPTION:Status: TENTATIVE\nWho: Lee Holden\, Kaitlin O'Toole\, Nadir Salam\nA sit-down interview needs the sound-controlled Energiakeskus studio\, NOT the Woodblock (Studio 2)\, which is a social-testimonial / vox-pop space (Gareth\, 21 Jul). Serialised after Lee's asset suite in the one studio: Marisa has Energiakeskus 10:00–12:45\, Lee's assets 12:45–14:45\, then this at 14:45. Kaitlin is off the main stage after 12:00 and Lee rolls straight in camera-ready off his assets\, so no extra makeup. Nadir operates. Lee's window runs to 2 Aug\, so there's slack if it needs to move.\nFull schedule: https://garethwinter-cpu.github.io/mindvalley-u-production/
END:VEVENT
